title: US holds on to win the Presidents Cup
text:
> Sports US holds on to win the Presidents Cup United States' Bubba Watson reacts after missing a putt on the 18th green during his singles match against International team player Thongchai Jaidee of Thailand at the Presidents Cup golf tournament at the Jack Nicklaus Golf Club Korea, in Incheon, South Korea, Sunday, Oct. 11, 2015.(AP Photo/Lee Jin-man)
